The paper covers a broad range of topics in machine learning, including statistical inference, algebraic and spectral methods, and PAC learning. These topics are all central to the field of machine learning and are likely to be covered in papers submitted to arXiv categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.ST (Statistics). Of these categories, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely, as they are the most general categories for papers on machine learning and artificial intelligence.
